py_test
-------

copy these files to ~/.vim/ftplugin/python
 - py_test.vim
 - README
 - py_test/py_test.py
 - py_test/filtercwd.py

add "filetype plugin on" to ~/.vimrc

restart vim

vim /path/to/test_file.py

put your cursor inside the body of a test method

\m will run that testcase

\t will run all tests in that file

use \q to view test output in the quickfix window. (\q again to dismiss
the quickfix window)

